<h1>HGV accident repairs</h1>
<p>If your vehicle is damaged in an accident, we&#8217;ll take care of the repair process from start to finish. We&#8217;re the only commercial vehicle body shop in the North Wales and North West equipped to deal with the heaviest commercial vehicle accidents.</p>
